results.name: Decimal expansion of 22*sin(Pi/22).
comment: The ratio of the perimeter of a regular 11-gon (hendecagon) to its diameter (largest diagonal).
Also least positive root of x^5 - 11x^4 - 484x^3 + 3993x^2 + 43923x - 161051.
results.author: _Rick L. Shepherd_, Jan 07 2017
